item.title: I need help!
item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

To get online, Your “NO-IP” is how people will login your server. To change your name go to your client file (client.java) and hit Ctrl + F, and type in setserver, change that to your NO-IP.

also make sure you have a source and not a client… Also click run instead of voule
